  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Each archetype receives 1-3 special duties or powers that reinforce their narrative function.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Some archetypes are passive observers, while others have direct influence on class events.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> These roles are distinct from skill-based advantages—they introduce a game mechanic.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📖</font> Archetypes &amp Their In-Class Roles</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Archetype</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Special Roles &amp Duties</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>How It Works</div>",
